The '''Greengairs Landfill''' is a [[landfill]] site in [[Scotland]] that receives non-hazardous household, commercial and industrial waste from the [[North Lanarkshire]] area.  Greengairs was opened in 1990 and features [[landfill gas]] collection systems which are used to generate [[electricity]] for export into the [[National Grid (UK)|National Grid]].

The landfill is owned and operated by [[FCC Environment]].

